  # Mastering the Art of Audio: How to Prompt Lyria 3 Like a Pro
  
  ![Mastering the Art of Audio: How to Prompt Lyria 3 Like a Pro image de l'article principal](https://www.creativefabrica.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/25/mastering-the-art-of-audio-how-to-prompt-lyria-3-article-145529396-1.png)
  
  _Publié le March 25, 2026 par [Linnea Holgersson de Creative Fabrica](https://www.creativefabrica.com/fr/the-artistry/author/linnea-2/)_
  
  166
  
  0
  
  0
  
  The launch of Lyria 3 marks a massive leap in how we communicate with AI to create music. Unlike previous models that required rigid technical jargon, Lyria 3 is built to understand the _nuance_ of musicality; from the gravelly texture of a soulful vocal to the specific “swing” of a 90s hip-hop beat. To get the most out of this model in [Creative Fabrica Studio](https://studio.creativefabrica.com/audio/lyria-3/), you need to move beyond simple descriptions and start thinking like a Producer.
  
  The secret to a “perfect” generation lies in **The Anchor Formula**: combining a clear **Genre & Era** with specific **Instrumentation** and a defined **Emotional Arc**. Because Lyria 3 can now handle tracks up to 3 minutes, it isn’t just looking for a “vibe”—it’s looking for a structure. By specifying how a song should evolve—such as starting with a solo acoustic guitar and building into a high-energy cinematic chorus—you give the model the roadmap it needs to create professional-grade compositions.
  
  # **The 4 Pillars of a High-Fidelity Prompt**
  
  To consistently hit that “studio-quality” mark, every prompt should touch on these four elements:
  
  1. **Genre & Era Fusion:** Don’t just say “Pop.” Say “Early 2000s Bubblegum Pop” or “Synthwave with a 1980s analog feel.” Lyria 3 excels at blending these styles, so feel free to experiment with “K-Pop vocals over a Motown-inspired rhythm.”
  2. **Vocal Character:** With Lyria 3’s breakthrough in vocal clarity, your descriptions matter. Specify the range (Soprano, Baritone), the tone (breathy, powerful, raspy), and the energy (laid-back groove vs. high-octane belt).
  3. **Dynamic Movement:** Use “action” words to describe the song’s flow. Tell the model to “crescendo,” “drop the drums at the 30-second mark,” or “transition from a stripped-back verse to an explosive finale.”
  4. **Lyrics & Phrasing:** If you want specific lines, use the **Lyrics:** tag. To create those professional “earworms,” you can even prompt for background effects like “call-and-response harmonies” or “echoed phrases in parentheses.”
  
  # **Pro-Tip for CF Studio AI Users**
  
  While Google’s native tools often lean toward 30-second clips, the [Lyria 3 integration in Studio AI](https://studio.creativefabrica.com/audio/lyria-3/) is built for full-scale creation. When writing your prompts here, think **long-form**. Describe the bridge, the chorus, and the fade-out. The more space you give the model to “breathe” in your description, the more professional your 3-minute track will sound.
  
  # **Create New Songs of your Favorite Genre**
  
  |     |     |
  | --- | --- |
  | **R&B** | **Prompt:** A slow, emotionally resonant R&B ballad. <br>**Vocal:** A powerful female soprano with a rich, gravelly texture in the lower register and a soaring, crystal-clear belt in the chorus. <br>**Structure:** Start with a melancholic solo grand piano; at 0:45, introduce a deep synth bass and slow-tempo 808 drums. <br>**Lyrics:** “The city lights are fading (fading), but I’m still standing here. Shadows grow long, but the rhythm is clear.” <br>**Atmosphere:** Intimate, soulful, and cinematic. 3-minute duration with a fading vocal ad-lib outro |
  | **Grunge** | **Prompt:** 1990s-style Grunge rock. <br>**Vocal:** A gritty, raspy male baritone with a “tired” and “unpolished” emotive delivery. <br>**Instrumentation:** Distorted, “fuzzy” electric guitar riffs and heavy, unquantized acoustic drums. <br>**Structure:** Quiet verse with a single guitar, transitioning into an explosive, high-energy chorus with crashing cymbals. <br>**Lyrics:** “Dust on the windshield, miles to go. Searching for a station on the radio.” <br>**Vibe:** Raw, rebellious, and nostalgic. |
  | **K-Pop** | **Prompt:** A high-energy, polished K-Pop anthem. <br>**Vocal:** Multiple female vocal tracks with sugary, bright tones, rapid-fire rhythmic delivery, and breathy “whisper” ad-libs in the background. <br>**Instrumentation:** Shiny FM synthesizers, heavy sub-bass, and complex percussion layers. <br>**Structure:** Fast-paced with a distinct “bridge” section featuring a half-time trap beat. <br>**Vibe:** Neon, futuristic, and chart-ready. Full 3-minute professional arrangement. |
  | **Gospel** | **Prompt:** A massive, uplifting Gospel anthem. <br>**Vocal:** A lead soulful tenor with a wide vibrato, backed by a layered 20-person choir providing call-and-response harmonies. <br>**Instrumentation:** A Hammond B3 organ with a rotary speaker effect and a steady, rhythmic tambourine. <br>**Structure:** Start with the lead vocal and organ, building into a full-choir crescendo with handclaps at the 2-minute mark. <br>**Vibe:** Spiritual, powerful, and soaring. |
  | **Pop** | **Prompt:** A shimmering Dream Pop soundscape. <br>**Vocal:** Soft, whisper-quiet female vocals drenched in “hall” reverb and delay for an otherworldly effect. <br>**Instrumentation:** Shimmering synth pads, a chorus-heavy electric guitar, and a minimalist electronic heartbeat rhythm. <br>**Structure:** An evolving 3-minute track that feels like it’s floating, with no hard transitions. <br>**Vibe:** Hazy, surreal, and immersive. |
  | **Country** | **Prompt:** A classic “Outlaw Country” storytelling track. <br>**Vocal:** A clear, twangy male baritone with a heavy southern accent and a focus on crisp lyrical enunciation. <br>**Instrumentation:** A steady acoustic guitar, a lonely “weeping” fiddle, and a subtle “train-beat” brushed snare drum. <br>**Lyrics:** “The highway is a ghost, and the moon is a dime. I’m just a man running out of time.” <br>**Vibe:** Authentic, dusty, and grounded. |
  | **Hip Hop** | **Prompt:** Gritty, “Golden Era” Hip Hop. <br>**Vocal:** Rhythmic, punchy male vocals with a confident, street-smart delivery and 90s-style flow. <br>**Instrumentation:** A dusty piano loop, a heavy-hitting boom-bap drum break with vinyl crackle, and scratched vocal samples in the hooks. <br>**Structure:** Two long verses separated by a melodic, scratched-in chorus. <br>**Vibe:** Urban, raw, and rhythmic |
  | **Metal** | **Prompt:** Dramatic Symphonic Metal. <br>**Vocal:** A classically trained operatic soprano with a wide range, hitting high crystalline notes over aggressive music. <br>**Instrumentation:** Rapid “double-kick” drumming, heavily distorted downtuned electric guitars, and a full orchestral string section. <br>**Structure:** Cinematic intro leading into a high-octane metal rhythm. <br>**Vibe:** Epic, dark, and theatrical |
  | **French Pop** | **Prompt:** A romantic, vintage-style French Pop song. <br>**Vocal:** A breathy, intimate female vocal with a playful “chic” delivery. <br>**Instrumentation:** A delicate upright piano, a rhythmic accordion, and a soft upright bass. <br>**Structure:** A charming, waltz-like 3/4 time signature that builds into a lush string-filled finale. <br>**Vibe:** Cinematic, Parisian, and nostalgic. |
  | **Bossa Nova** | **Prompt:** A breezy, sophisticated Bossa Nova track. <br>**Vocal:** A gentle male and female duet singing in Portuguese with soft, airy delivery. <br>**Instrumentation:** A nylon-string acoustic guitar playing rhythmic syncopation, a warm upright bass, and light “shaker” percussion. <br>**Structure:** 8-bar guitar intro, alternating verses between the two singers, and a synchronized harmonic chorus. <br>**Atmosphere:** Relaxed, sun-drenched, and elegant. |
  
  # **Experiment with Genre Mashups**
  
  |     |     |
  | --- | --- |
  | **Cyberpunk Jazz** | **Prompt:** A fusion of 1920s jazz swing and futuristic cyberpunk soundscapes. <br>**Core:** A fast-tempo acoustic upright bass and muted trumpet playing a classic “bebop” rhythm. <br>**Synthesized Elements:** Overlaid with heavy, resonant 808 sub-bass hits and glitchy, neon-synth textures. <br>**Structure:** A smooth jazz introduction; at 1:15, a heavy electronic “drop” blends the two styles seamlessly. <br>**Lyrics:** “Neon streets, and a lonely sax, singing blues on a glitchy track.” 3-minute professional arrangement |
  | **Classical Lo-Fi** | **Prompt:** Melancholic Classical music meets Lo-Fi Study Beats. <br>**Core:** A highly detailed, sad solo violin melody with a deep sense of emotive longing. <br>**Mashup:** This melody is sampled and layered over a dusty, textured hip-hop drum break (vinyl crackle, tape hiss). <br>**Structure:** 3 minutes of evolving, chilled, and dusty classical instrumentation. <br>**Lyrics:** (No vocals). <br>**Vibe:** Nostalgic, focus-heavy, and dusty. |
  | **Motown EDM** | **Prompt:** The smooth production of 1960s Motown blended with modern House music energy. <br>**Core:** Authentic, rhythmic brass sections and a clean, funky electric guitar riff. <br>**Vocal:** A powerful, layered female soul vocal track. <br>**Mashup:** The entire composition is driven by a 128 BPM four-on-the-floor EDM kick drum and subtle synth-bass pulsing. <br>**Structure:** Evolving song structure starting with a “soul” vibe and building into an “anthem” finale. |
  | **Medieval Rock** | **Prompt:** Medieval folk meeting 1970s classic rock. <br>**Vocal:** A masculine, choral-style vocal chant, like monks in a monastery. <br>**Instrumentation:** Lutes, recorders, and a hurdy-gurdy playing ancient melodies. <br>**Mashup:** These are suddenly overtaken by a screaming distorted electric guitar and a heavy, pounding rock drum beat. <br>**Vibe:** Epic, rebellious, and folk-heavy. |
  | **Afrobeat Synthwave** | **Prompt:** A blend of the hypnotic, driving percussion of Nigerian Afrobeat and the shimmering, nostalgic textures of 1980s Synthwave. <br>**Core:** A fast, multi-layered percussion loop (talking drums, congas). <br>**Mashup:** A driving, arpeggiated synth-bass and bright, shimmering “Miami” synths play the lead melody. <br>**Structure:** The percussion never stops, while the synths evolve the melody for 3 minutes. <br>**Vibe:** Summer, high-energy, and retro-futuristic. |
  | **Bluegrass Techno** | **Prompt:** A fast-paced Bluegrass stomp meets modern Berlin Techno. <br>**Core:** Extremely fast banjo picking, a rapid fiddle melody, and a prominent acoustic guitar. <br>**Mashup:** These acoustic instruments are perfectly synchronized to a hard-hitting, minimalist 135 BPM four-on-the-floor electronic kick drum. <br>**Structure:** The acoustic instruments provide the melodic “texture” over a constant, heavy-club techno pulse. |
  | **Reggaeton Baroque** | **Prompt:** 17th-century Baroque meeting 21st-century Latin Urban. <br>**Core:** A highly detailed, complex harpsichord and violin “sonata” composition. <br>**Mashup:** This entire piece is dropped over a classic, deep Reggaeton “Dembow” (BOOM-ch-BOOM-ch) rhythm with heavy bass. <br>**Vibe:** Unexpected, regal, and urban. |
  | **Flamenco Trap** | **Prompt:** Rapid-fire Spanish Flamenco guitar blended with the high-fidelity percussion of modern Trap. <br>**Core:** A masterful, emotive Spanish guitar performance (rapid strumming, “palmas” handclaps). <br>**Mashup:** The guitar performance is perfectly cut and sampled over sharp, triplet hi-hats, a hard “snare-rim” sound, and a massive 808 sub-bass “boom.” <br>**Vocal:** Intermittent Spanish vocal ad-libs (“¡Olé!”). <br>**Vibe:** Passionate, modern, and aggressive. |
  | **Viking Ambient Soundscape** | **Prompt:** A 3-minute evolving cinematic journey blending Ambient drone and historical Viking music. <br>**Core:** Deep, guttural throat-singing chants and a solitary, low “Lyre” (ancient harp) melody. <br>**Mashup:** These elements are synthesized into massive, evolving electronic pads that feel like ice or space. <br>**Atmosphere:** Distant storm wind, clanging metal percussion (swords/hammers), and a sense of vast, dark history. <br>**Vibe:** Ancient, powerful, and immersive |
  | **Surf Rock Disco** | **Prompt:** A synthesis of the beach energy of 1960s Surf Rock and the high-society groove of 1970s Disco. <br>**Core:** Reverb-heavy “surf” electric guitar playing rapid, twangy melodies. <br>**Mashup**: The instrumentation is layered over a funky, high-octane 120 BPM disco beat with a complex “slap-bass” groove and rhythmic brass stabs. <br>**Vibe:** Beach, party, and retro |
  
  # **Cinematic Scores & Soundscapes**
  
  |     |     |
  | --- | --- |
  | **Event Horizon: The Long Void** | **Prompt:** A 3-minute evolving interstellar ambient score. <br>**Phase 1 (0:00-1:00):** Deep, oscillating sub-bass drones and isolated, crystalline “star-twinkle” synth pings. <br>**Phase 2 (1:00-2:15):** A slow build-up of sweeping orchestral strings and a low, resonant brass section. <br>**Phase 3 (Final):** A massive, awe-inspiring crescendo with a layered celestial choir. <br>**Vibe:** Vast, majestic, and high-fidelity. |
  | **Neon Shadows: Case No. 402** | **Prompt:** Moody, rain-soaked Jazz-Noir for a 3-minute mystery scene. <br>**Instrumentation:** A lonely, reverb-heavy trumpet lead, a brushed snare drum rhythm, and a dark upright bass. <br>**Atmosphere:** Add subtle foley sounds of rain hitting pavement and distant city sirens. <br>**Structure:** Start with the solo trumpet; gradually introduce a melancholic piano at the 1:30 mark. <br>**Vibe:** Sophisticated, mysterious, and cinematic.. |
  | **Kingdom of the Iron Rose** | **Prompt:** A 3-minute epic orchestral theme for a fantasy hero. <br>**Core:** Soaring French horns and a rhythmic, driving string section (staccato). <br>**Progression:** The track starts with a single flute melody, building into a full symphonic explosion with tribal war drums and crashing cymbals. <br>**Dynamics:** Use frequent “swells” and dramatic pauses. <br>**Vibe:** Heroic, grand, and legendary. |
  | **The House on Blackwood Lane** | **Prompt:** A high-tension 3-minute suspense score. <br>**Instrumentation:** Dissonant, screeching violins, a rhythmic “ticking clock” percussion, and sudden, low-frequency sub-bass “hits.” <br>**Arc:** The tempo feels like it’s subtly increasing, creating an “anxious” feeling. At 2:30, the music drops to a near-silent, eerie high-pitched tone before a final, loud orchestral “jump-scare.” <br>**Vibe:** Terrifying, claustrophobic, and modern. |
  | **Wild Earth: The Canopy** | **Prompt:** A 3-minute peaceful, organic soundscape. <br>**Instrumentation:** Finger-picked acoustic guitar, soft woodwind melodies (flute/oboe), and gentle “glockenspiel” highlights. <br>**Atmosphere:** Layer in very faint sounds of birds chirping and wind through leaves. <br>**Progression:** A light, airy build-up that feels like a sunrise, ending on a warm, major-key piano chord. <br>**Vibe:** Serene, beautiful, and pristine |
  | **Outrun: Tokyo Drift 2088** | **Prompt:** A high-octane 3-minute 1980s-inspired synth score. <br>**Instrumentation:** Driving analog arpeggios, “Linndrum” style electronic percussion, and a heroic “lead” synth. <br>**Structure:** Keep the energy high (120 BPM) with a dramatic “breakdown” section at 1:45 featuring a solo synth-bass before the full beat returns. <br>**Vibe:** Fast-paced, nostalgic, and high-energy |
  | **The Last Signal: Year Zero** | **Prompt:** A 3-minute desolate, post-apocalyptic ambient track. <br>**Instrumentation:** Distant, distorted electric guitar feedback, clanging metal-on-metal percussion, and a lonely, wind-like synth drone. <br>**Atmosphere:** Use “wide” stereo reverb to create a sense of massive, empty space. <br>**Vocal:** Faint, wordless female vocal hums in the distance. <br>**Vibe:** Lonely, gritty, and hollow |
  | **Clockwork Rebellion** | **Prompt**: A rhythmic, 3-minute industrial track. <br>**Core**: Rhythmic steam-release sounds, heavy metallic clangs, and “clockwork” gears turning. <br>**Melody**: A low, rhythmic cello section playing a repetitive, mechanical motif. <br>**Progression:** The “machine” starts slow and speeds up throughout the 3 minutes, ending with a massive steam-venting sound.<br>**Vibe:** Mechanical, heavy, and rhythmic |
  | **Abyssal Silence** | **Prompt:** A 3-minute submerged, immersive ambient piece. <br>**Instrumentation:** Muffled, “underwater” piano chords with long sustains, bubbling foley effects, and deep, pulsing “heartbeat” bass. <br>**Frequency:** Filter out high-end frequencies to simulate being deep under the sea. <br>**Vibe:** Calm, mysterious, and blue |
  | **Horizon Technologies: The Future Now** | **Prompt:** A 3-minute professional, building corporate anthem. <br>**Instrumentation:** Clean, palm-muted electric guitar, a steady “kick-clap” beat, and bright, optimistic piano stabs. <br>**Progression:** Designed to support a long presentation; starts minimal and adds layers every 30 seconds to maintain engagement. <br>**Vibe:** Positive, innovative, and clean |
  
  # **TikTok/Reels OST**
  
  |     |     |
  | --- | --- |
  | **Here I am** | **Prompt:** A strut-worthy, modern Funk-Pop anthem. <br>**Vocal:** A smooth, confident female vocal track with slight reverb and processed “vocal chops” as rhythmic accents. <br>**Instrumentation:** A deep, “walking” slap-bassline, tight “four-on-the-floor” electronic kick drum, and occasional rhythmic brass section hits. <br>**Structure:** The energy must stay high and constant (110 BPM) for the full generation. <br>**Vibe:** Funky, self-assured, and perfect for walking transitions |
  | **Cooking tutorial** | **Prompt:** Upbeat, happy, and whimsical acoustic pop. <br>**Instrumentation:** High-fidelity glockenspiel (bells) playing a catchy melody, handclaps on the backbeat, and a soft, rhythmic acoustic guitar strumming. <br>**Vibe:** Playful, positive, and clean. (No vocals are needed; the instrumentation provides the melody). |
  | **Unboxing** | **Prompt:** Minimalist, futuristic IDM (Intelligent Dance Music). <br>**Instrumentation:** A highly detailed collection of crisp, complex “blip” and “click” percussion (textured to sound digital). <br>**Synthesized Elements:** A deep, pulsing analog synth-bass drone providing an underlying “heartbeat.” <br>**Vibe:** Sleek, high-tech, and futuristic. Designed to sound like the inside of a server |
  | **Sports Reel** | **Prompt:** High-octane, modern Nu-Metal. <br>**Vocal:** An aggressive, shouting (but rhythmic) male vocal lead, layered for density. <br>**Instrumentation:** Fast, complex double-kick drumming, screaming high-register electric guitar solos, and heavily distorted “chugging” rhythm guitars. <br>**Vibe:** Aggressive, kinetic, and intense (140+ BPM). |
  | **ASMR** | **Prompt:** Extremely soft, minimal Ambient music designed for pure relaxation. <br>**Core Elements:** Pure sine-wave tones and gentle “wind chime” textures, filtered to remove all high frequencies for a “submerged” effect. <br>**Foley:** Add very faint foley sounds of rain hitting glass or a soft crackling fire. <br>**Vibe:** Calming, tranquil, and ethereal |
  | **High Fashion** | **Prompt:** Hypnotic and deep modern House music. <br>**Core:** A consistent, deep “club-ready” 124 BPM four-on-the-floor kick drum. <br>**Synth:** A hypnotic, single-note resonant synth-lead pattern that repeats. <br>**Foley/Mashup:** Rhythmic “shutter click” camera sounds synthesized into the percussion loop. <br>**Vocal:** Intermittent processed vocal shouts (“Work!”). <br>**Vibe:** Sleek, confident, and rhythmic |
  | **The Big Reveal** | **Prompt:** Orchestral and dramatic. <br>**Structure:** Starts with 5 seconds of extreme silence/soft ambient drone. <br>**Mashup:** A sudden, overwhelming orchestral “hit” or “Ta-Da” chord with screaming brass, crashing cymbals, and a deep bass-drum boom. (Prompt requires specific timing logic in Lyria 3) |
  | **Travel Montage** | **Prompt:** Upbeat Tropical House for vacation content. <br>**Core:** A modern four-on-the-floor kick drum rhythm. <br>**Instrumentation:** Melodic steel drums and a bright pan-flute synth playing a joyful, repeating lead melody. <br>**Vocal:** Highly processed “vocal chops” synthesized to play the chord progression. <br>**Vibe:** Sunny, joyful, and rhythmic (115 BPM). |
  | **Gaming Reel** | **Prompt:** High-fidelity 8-bit Chiptune (sounding like a classic NES or Arcade game). <br>**Instrumentation:** Pure square-wave and pulse-wave synthesizers playing a fast, melodic “heroic level theme.” <br>**Foley/Mashup:** Synthesized sound effects of coins collected or jumps incorporated into the rhythm. <br>**Vibe:** Playful, energetic, and nostalgic |
  | **Spooky Comedy Skit** | **Prompt:** Whimsical and quirky orchestral “Halloween” comedy. <br>**Instrumentation:** A single “stumbling” bassoon rhythm and a quirky, dissonant “circus organ” melody playing the main theme. <br>**Progression:** The track feels unsteady and clumsy. <br>**Foley:** Add subtle “creaking door” foley sounds on the backbeat. <br>**Vibe:** Cheesy, fun, and spooky |
  
  # **B** **usiness/Marketing Content**
  
  |     |     |
  | --- | --- |
  | **Podcast Intro** | **Prompt**: A 45-second sophisticated Jazz-Fusion intro. <br>**Instrumentation**: Clean electric guitar with a “chorus” effect, a warm upright bass, and a steady, light “ride-cymbal” drum groove. <br>**Structure**: Start with a 5-second musical “sting,” then lower the volume (ducking) of the instruments to a “background bed” level for the host to speak over. <br>**Vibe**: Intellectual, smooth, and welcoming. |
  | **Real Estate Tour** | **Prompt:** High-end, “Architectural” Ambient music. <br>**Instrumentation:** A minimalist, “glassy” electric piano melody with long delays and a soft, pulsing sub-bass. <br>**Progression:** The track should feel “spacious” and “airy,” with no sudden changes in volume or tempo. <br>**Vibe:** Sophisticated, clean, and expensive. Designed to complement high-definition interior videography |
  | **App UI Sounds** | **Prompt:** A collection of short, 2-to-5 second melodic “earcons” (icons for the ear). <br>**Sound Profile:** High-pitched, crystalline synth “shimmers” and “blips.” <br>**Variation:** One sound for “Success” (rising major chord), one for “Notification” (neutral “ding”), and one for “Processing” (a soft, rhythmic pulse). <br>**Vibe:** High-tech, minimalist, and user-friendly |
  | **Gym Ad** | **Prompt:** A driving, aggressive 140 BPM Techno track. <br>**Core:** A heavy, distorted “industrial” kick drum and a repetitive, acid-style synth-bass sequence. <br>**Progression:** The track should build in “density” every 30 seconds, adding layers of high-hats and white-noise “whoosh” effects to increase the user’s heart rate. <br>**Vibe:** Relentless, energetic, and powerful |
  | **Hold Music** | **Prompt:** A classic, polite, and non-repetitive Bossa Nova track for business telephony. <br>**Instrumentation:** Nylon-string guitar, soft flute melody, and light “shaker” percussion. <br>**Dynamics:** Keep the “brightness” setting at medium-low (0.4) to ensure the music stays pleasant over phone speakers. <br>**Vibe:** Patient, calm, and professional. 3-minute duration to avoid a short, annoying loop |
  | **Educational Experience** | **Prompt:** A clean, mid-tempo (100 BPM) instrumental for a science or history video. <br>**Instrumentation:** Soft marimba notes, a light “shuffling” percussion, and a warm synth-pad for atmosphere. <br>**Structure:** The melody is repetitive and steady, designed to sit underneath a complex voiceover without competing for the listener’s attention. <br>**Vibe:** Curious, objective, and rhythmic |
  | **Wellness Guide** | **Prompt:** 3 minutes of deep-immersion relaxation music. <br>**Core:** A constant, very low-frequency “Om” drone (60Hz) and soft, ethereal vocal “oohs” that fade in and out. <br>**Instrumentation:** Distant singing bowls and a very slow, single-note piano melody with massive reverb. <br>**Vibe:** Zen, tranquil, and restorative. |
  | **Tech Pitch** | **Prompt:** A building, cinematic electronic track for a startup presentation. <br>**Instrumentation:** Starts with a rhythmic, digital “heartbeat” synth. At 1:00, add driving orchestral strings and a clean electric bass. <br>**Arc:** The energy should peak at the 2:30 mark with a “heroic” synth lead before a clean, abrupt finish. <br>**Vibe:** Innovative, urgent, and successful. |
  | **Study with me** | **Prompt:** Classic “Chillhop” for long-duration focus. <br>**Instrumentation:** A dusty, sampled-sounding Rhodes piano loop and a lazy, swinging hip-hop drum beat. <br>**Atmosphere:** Add a subtle “vinyl crackle” foley layer and the sound of distant muffled city rain. <br>**Vibe:** Relaxed, nostalgic, and perfect for a “Study With Me” stream |
  | **Brand Sound Logo** | **Prompt:** A 5-second ultra-high-fidelity “brand sound.” <br>**Composition:** A fast, 4-note rising glissando on a crystalline synthesizer ending on a powerful, resonant “gong” hit. <br>**Texture:** The sound should feel “wide” and “premium,” using the full stereo spectrum. <br>**Vibe:** Modern, memorable, and high-end. |
  
